StepMania To Quaver¶

class reamber.algorithms.convert.SMToQua.SMToQua¶

Bases: object

static convert(sm: reamber.sm.SMMapSetObj.SMMapSetObj) → List[reamber.quaver.QuaMapObj.QuaMapObj]¶

Converts a SMMapset to possibly multiple quaver maps

Note that a mapset contains maps, so a list would be expected. SMMap conversion is not possible due to lack of SMMapset Metadata

Parameters

sm – SM Mapset

Returns

List of Quaver Maps
